===========================================================
OVERVIEW
-----------------------------------------------------------
CBB Model v4 is a fully automated NCAA basketball betting
model that:

1. Pulls efficiency ratings (BartTorvik)
2. Cleans and structures advanced metrics
3. Projects game-level spreads and totals
4. Uses structurally weighted spread construction
5. Applies home court + recency adjustments
6. Applies weighted head-to-head (H2H) matchup adjustments
7. Applies dynamic market-mean total bias anchoring
8. Calibrates win probability curve (logistic K)
9. Pulls live NCAA odds via The Odds API (Consensus)
10. Normalizes team names deterministically
11. Computes market edge vs projections
12. Outputs only qualified +EV bets
13. Exports full daily engine slate for reporting
14. Automatically syncs outputs to Google Sheets
15. Includes validated historical backtesting engine

The system is modular, automated, and production-stable.

